verbose_text: Of 362 variants that bind NBS strongly, 261 are NBS specific (i.e., no parS binding, magenta box), 19 show strong NBS binding but weak-to-medium parS binding (pink box), and 82 dual-specificity variants that bind both parS and NBS (black box) (XREF_FIG C).
